  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study will determine if Xiaoshuanchangrong (XSCR) capsule will improve recovery from an
      acute stroke. The study is designed to look at both overall recovery and recovery of motor
      function, for example muscle strength and coordination.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
